Mikkel Ricky Catalog Search
===========================


This extension makes it possible to give priotity to select attributes
when searching product catalog. The assigned priorities are used to
make the select attributes have more weight when computing product
relevance.


Installation
------------

1. Copy files to Magento directory.
2. Clear cache.

The extension creates a new database table,
mikkelrickycatalogsearch_fulltext, for storing fulltext indexing
data. Please check that this table exists after installation.


Configuration
-------------

System > Configuration > Catalog > Catalog > Mikkel Ricky Catalog Search

3 sets of weighted attributes can be defined: select attributes and
assign weight below attribute list.
